  "description": "<p><strong>Role: Infant Educator</strong></p><p><strong>AOP Childcare Centre</strong></p><p><strong>5 day | 7am - 7pm Rotate shift is a MUST</strong></p><p><strong>Entitled to AWS + Performance Bonus</strong></p><p><strong>Work location: Punggol / Bartley / Tampines </strong></p><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Obtained at least a Certificate in Infant Care (CIT), Advanced Certificate in Early Years (ACEY), Higher Certificate in Infant Care (HCIC), or its equivalent</strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Plan and carry out the daily programme, developmental and care-giving tasks as assigned</li><li>Attend to the health, hygiene and safety needs of the infants</li><li>Create a safe environment and provide the best possible care to infants under their care</li><li>Build and maintain good rapport with parents</li></ul><p><br />Tai Jia Seng Reg No: R26159755</p><p>The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279<br /></p><p></p></p>",
